Sns.Message: {"events": [{"text": "Now you bring her around", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "7793091bb176813800690cb0ee76263b"}, {"text": "Just to shut me down", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "c3c59d7be524753668195f0a67c4583e"}, {"text": "Show her off like she's a new trophy", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "2560b2c7fc8788716e78fe1d7327c48d"}, {"text": "And I know if you were true", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "358e70a1c4c0714587889e89cc11b8c2"}, {"text": "There's no damn way that you", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "95b3d390175b8204ecd6f79e195a57af"}, {"text": "Could fall in love with somebody that quickly", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "94f236c639b1fd0287a283284d3f0627"}, {"text": "Ain't it funny", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "b2f946955232da1d860d4a0646db8a4f"}, {"text": "All the twisted games", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "07b63279f791ea997f8fb381674e1c45"}, {"text": "All the questions you used to avoid?", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "15fa3d79d316837ab4c626978dca6eed"}, {"text": "Ain't it funny?", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "09e36bf390c5163d803d4857c5bf1fba"}, {"text": "Remember I brought her up", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "b906eee90a2f119b5f282efc6b04e304"}, {"text": "And you told me I was paranoid", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "8c601971e64a730d376d3977d196568a"}, {"text": "You betrayed me", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "b7cad148c4ff5fdfbe0094fc6378e5e6"}, {"text": "And I know that you'll never feel sorry", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "0a4df6863c96a3a05c00531cf1b152d8"}, {"text": "For the way I hurt, yeah", "type": "song", "song_name": "traitor", "id": "15bc45cec37cb950f85f1c605074808c"}]}
